{"tid":1557192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喇沙舊生同盧偉聰割席!!!","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:37:30.000Z","uid":8648,"like":376,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"46d4269ab31a7cf10b32de742d54cd99074119e5","tid":1557192,"uid":8648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【逆權運動】盧偉聰師弟促檢控濫暴警員 喇沙仔音樂會上拉橫額籲「捍衞良知」</span></span><br />\n警察驅散市民屢被批評用暴力鎮壓，8.31更在港鐵太子站內無差別襲擊市民，掀起恐慌，但警務處處長盧偉聰至今仍「龜縮」，沒有就事件向市民公開交代。盧的母校喇沙書院有舊生在昨晚舉行的舊生音樂會上，就拉起寫有「克己復禮 捍衞良知」標語，強烈譴責師兄盧偉聰的警隊濫權。<br />\n昨晚舉行的喇沙書院舊生音樂會上，舊生們用不同方法聲援這場逆權運動，除了樂團表演奏出抗爭名曲《Do You Hear the People Sing?》外，多位舊生在台上亦拉起印有「克己復禮 捍衞良知」的黑色橫額，並稱代表喇沙書院中樂團舊生，嚴厲譴責警隊，必須立即停止所有暴行，「無數次濫權濫暴、721及831恐襲，必須檢控干犯相關暴行的警員」。<br />\n中樂團舊生亦對喇沙書院舊生會予以強烈關注，認為在現時大是大非的社會議題上，舊生會應承擔更多社會責任，及表達更多關注，強調「藍黃是政見，黑白是良知，喇沙仔可以接受政治光譜嘅不同，但絕不接受泯滅良知、是非不分」。舊生代表稱，有人會認為學校、音樂不應與政治扯上關係，但事實上政治會自動找上你，並舉例指上周大專學界發動罷課，不論是罷課學生、到場支持的畢業生均受到不同程度的打壓，立法會議員何君堯更以監察為名恐嚇為實發公開信予各校意圖打壓罷課，直言「儘管不是每一個人都認同我們這次的做法，但我們自覺身為喇沙仔應為社會不公義發聲」，並向受影響觀眾致歉。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190908&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60022616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190908%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60022616&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=fd3ada41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190908%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60022616&h=4fead069\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190908&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60022616</a><br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16afdae7d8bb8a3aacf38b5e34beb8380e8c416","tid":1557192,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫我推上熱門</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吾係狗 吾係香港政府 要全世界對準政權 果個人叫中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【海外文宣戰線】一個外國巴同我講ge野 The enemy is the communist party.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89351fad16eb681a68de23b948abc2f968b2420c","tid":1557192,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"807a445584aa87e7254a212838954e8e5033b4c5","tid":1557192,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23acea4d7f072d6d81f6125d9d7c1902a4861cee","tid":1557192,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b2f6d557f69d13422e08bf026d774b9d370a54","tid":1557192,"uid":8648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e16afdae7d8bb8a3aacf38b5e34beb8380e8c416","tid":1557192,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫我推上熱門</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br /